  "info": {
    "title": "Microphone-​Voice Amplifier",
    "description": "Microphone-Voice Amplifier: Your Professional Sound Boost\nTurn your Android device into a powerful, real-time voice amplifier and Bluetooth microphone. Whether you need a hearing amplifier for clearer conversations, a live microphone to speaker for announcements, presentations, meetings, and guiding tours, or a high-quality audio recorder, this all-in-one sound amplifier app is your versatile solution. It features advanced noise reduction, flexible background play, and a variety of microphone styles to choose from.\n\nUse our Microphone Amplifier, you can get\n- Multiple Microphone styles to pick up\n- Easy switch to Bluetooth Microphone Amplifier\n- Build-in high-quality live audio recorder\n- Live sound amplification with noise reduction\n- Keep the amplifier running in the background or with the screen off\n\n🎯 Why Choose Our Microphone Amplifier?\n• Live Voice & Sound Amplification with Noise Reduction:\nExperience crystal-clear, real-time (live sound) enhancement. The built-in noise reduction feature minimizes background interference, ensuring your voice is projected crisply. It's more than a simple sound booster; it's a professional audio amplifier device.\n• Bluetooth Microphone Amplifier:\nUse your phone as a wireless Bluetooth microphone for speakers. Perfect for presentations, teaching, meetings, and guiding tours, providing stable wireless audio transmission.\n• Hearing Assistance & Clear Listening:\nFunctions as a practical listening amplifier and hearing amplifier app. The noise reduction technology helps you hear speech and sounds more clearly in noisy environments like restaurants or crowded places.\n• Professional Audio Recorder:\nCapture important moments, meetings, or creative ideas with the built-in high-quality live audio recorder.\n• Customizable Sound with Multiple Microphone Styles:\nAdjust settings and choose from various virtual microphone styles (e.g., studio, vocal boost, ambient) to create your ideal professional sound amplifier experience.\n\n🌟 Key Features as Your Sound Amplifier Device:\n✔ Live Sound & Microphone Amplifier: Real-time voice amplification with noise suppression for clear projection.\n✔ Background Play Function: Keep the amplifier running while using other apps or with your screen off, perfect for extended events or personal listening.\n✔ Multiple Microphone Styles: Select from different audio pickup patterns and styles to match your scenario (speech, singing, broadcasting).\n✔ Bluetooth Speaker Connect: Seamlessly connect to any Bluetooth speaker or headset.\n✔ Voice Recorder & Sound Recorder: Capture audio clearly with the integrated audio recorder.\n✔ Sound Booster & Audio Booster: Enhance volume and clarity for any audio source.\n\n📱 How to Use This Microphone Amplifier App in 3 Steps:\nConnect your headphones or any Bluetooth speaker.\nLaunch the app, select your preferred microphone style, and tap start – your phone instantly becomes a live microphone.\nAdjust the sound amplifier and noise reduction settings for clear listening or loud speaking. You can even switch to other apps while it runs in the background.\n\nIdeal as a hearing device amplifier, microphone-to-speaker tool, or professional voice recorder, this sound amplifier device adapts to your needs. Its background play capability allows for uninterrupted use during long gatherings or personal listening sessions. It's the essential voice amplifier app for everyday clarity and versatile audio projects.\nUse the Live Voice Amplifier now and transform your phone into a powerful, intelligent audio tool!\n\nDisclaimer: This sound amplifier app is designed for audio enhancement, communication assistance, and personal use. It is not a certified medical hearing aid device. Please consult a healthcare professional for medical hearing issues.\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://sites.google.com/view/wirelessmicrophone-privacypoli/\nTerms of user: https://sites.google.com/view/wirelessmicrophone-termsofuser/\nYou can contact us with: xiangdong.li.ldx@gmail.com",
